title: e.l.f. Eye Primer and Liner Sealer, Natural, 0.24 Ounce
description: The Prime side sets your eyeshadow in so your color won't fade, bleed or crease. The Liner side transforms your favorite eye shadow into a waterproof, smudge-proof liquid liner with this unique clear liquid and built-in felt tip precision eyeliner brush. Now you can have your eye makeup lasting longer for no fuss no budge color.

title: Bed Head Deep Waver
description: Want frizz-free, bouncy waves that last all day and night, then you will love bed head's 3/4 inch tourmaline ceramic deep waver. tourmaline technology leaves you with frizz-free shiny styles. ceramic technology provides high, even heat that penetrates hair from the inside-out, helping hair retain natural moisture for “frizz-free” styles.

title: China Glaze Lorelei's Tiara 80774 Nail Polish
description: China Glaze Lorelei's Tiara is a silver with blue glitter in a clear base nail polish color. The silver glitter is small glitter, the blue is larger hex glitter. China Glaze Eye Candy Collection, Winter 2011.
